---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Maren Stokes - her journey in STEM, leadership, and continuous learning."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <SectionHeading
      title="About Me"
      subtitle="My journey through STEM, leadership, and continuous learning"
    />

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="bio-section">
        <p class="lead">
          Ever since I was introduced to STEM at a young age, I've been driven by curiosity.
          I started coding in <strong>fourth grade</strong>, and what began as simple experimentation
          eventually grew into a deeper love for <strong>machine learning, math, and physics</strong>.
          Over time, I've become especially interested in how theoretical thinking and technical
          problem-solving connect to real-world impact.
        </p>

        <p>
          I've had the chance to continue that journey through <strong>UT Austin Computer Science
          machine learning summer programs</strong>, advanced coursework, and independent exploration.
          At the same time, my experiences in <strong>leadership, debate, and civic engagement</strong>
          have helped me grow not just as a student, but as someone who values community,
          responsibility, and voice.
        </p>

        <p>
          I love learning, improving, and staying open to wherever curiosity leads — whether that's
          understanding complex systems in physics, developing smarter technology, or working where
          STEM and leadership intersect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="values-section">
        <h3 class="subsection-title">What Drives Me</h3>

        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-item">
            <h4>Curiosity</h4>
            <p>
              A constant desire to understand how things work, from the mathematical structures
              that govern our universe to the intelligent systems we're building for the future.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-item">
            <h4>Growth</h4>
            <p>
              Challenging myself through rigorous coursework, competitive programs, and
              leadership opportunities that push me beyond my comfort zone.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-item">
            <h4>Community</h4>
            <p>
              Building spaces where people can think, collaborate, and grow together —
              whether through NHI, Math Honor Society, or Model UN.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-item">
            <h4>Impact</h4>
            <p>
              Connecting theoretical knowledge to real-world applications, making sure
              what I learn can contribute to solving meaningful problems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="interests-section">
        <h3 class="subsection-title">Beyond the Classroom</h3>

        <p>
          While academics and STEM are central to my life, I also find fulfillment in:
        </p>

        <ul class="interests-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Public Speaking & Debate</strong> — Through NHI and Model UN,
            developing confidence in presenting ideas and engaging in thoughtful discourse
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Tennis</strong> — Building discipline, resilience, and the mental
            toughness that comes from competitive athletics
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Policy & Government</strong> — Understanding how systems work at a
            civic level and how leadership shapes communities
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Continuous Learning</strong> — Whether it's a new programming language,
            a physics concept, or a leadership framework, I'm always exploring
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="looking-forward">
        <h3 class="subsection-title">Looking Forward</h3>

        <p>
          As I prepare for college and beyond, I'm excited to continue exploring the
          intersection of mathematics, physics, and computer science. I'm particularly
          interested in how machine learning and applied mathematics can help us better
          understand complex systems and create meaningful technological advances.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm looking for opportunities to learn from brilliant people, contribute to
          research that matters, and continue developing both my technical skills and
          my ability to lead and communicate effectively.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-3xl);
  }

  .bio-section p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .bio-section .lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }

  .bio-section strong {
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .subsection-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .value-item {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.08);
  }

  .value-item h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .value-item p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .interests-section p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .interests-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .interests-list li {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    position: relative;
  }

  .interests-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .interests-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .looking-forward p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bio-section .lead {
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    }

    .bio-section p,
    .interests-section p,
    .looking-forward p {
      font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .value-item {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
